==Trivia==
* A {{Wp|Banshee}} is a female spirit in {{Wp|irish folklore}}. Her shrieks are said to foreshadow the imminent passing of a family member.
* Banshees become translucent when moving or turning but become solid when standing still, this mechanic may have been inspired from Super Mario's {{Wp|Boo (character)|Boo}}.

